info: Rating, 2 stars,  · February 2024,  · Stayed a few nights
rating_comment:
The host was really responsive and clear throughout the whole process.
But the place is filthy. There were stains all over the place including the bed sheet.
The bathroom was very unclean with hair and stains everywhere.
This place definitely needs a revamp.

info: Rating, 5 stars,  · July 2023,  · Stayed one night
Rating, 5 stars,  · March 2023,  · Stayed a few nights
rating_comment:
Tanvir is a great host. All staffs are very friendly. Room is neat and clean, away from busy street, surrounded by restaurants and shops.
It is a walk distance from my local principal’s office. I do enjoy the daily 1.5km walk.
Plus the top floor restaurant is a great place with various food available (I continued dining in the restaurant for 4 days, always finished the food).
In short, it is a cost-effective and beyond expectation stay during my this time Dhaka adventure. Highly recommended.

info: Rating, 4 stars,  · January 2023,  · Stayed a few nights
rating_comment:
Staff are very good, well trained, proactive, friendly and helpful. 24 hours service. The room is very clean and comfortable. The location is good.
The only thing I would suggest to the management is if they could use /put another layer of glass (soundproof glass ) to avoid outside noise.

rating_comment: Host Tanvir was quite friendly and all staffs were well behaved. Pleasure to stay.Also thanks dfor arranging parking as well.
